data.description: New Price improvement on this Dixie Springs Listing,, just minutes from Sand Hollow Reservoir and Resort and NO HOA.  This home was built new in 2017.  The home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, open concept floorplan, chefs kitchen with granite countertops and all appliances remaining with the home.  Other features of the home include tile flooring,  upgraded cabinets, sola-tube skylights, upgraded lighting and many more top end finishes.  You'll love the large backyard which definitely has space for a pool.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement. Call the Listing Agent today to schedule your own private showing.
